"title": "4333: gold",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4333: gold",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The most valuable of all metals, gold was indicative of wealth and prosperity in biblical times. It had a wide variety of uses and was employed extensively in both the tabernacle and the temple.</p>\n<h2>Gold was of great value</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:17\">ISA 60:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:18-Josh6:19\">JOS 6:18–6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">JOS 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:1-1Kgs20:6\">1KI 20:1–20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:8\">2KI 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:14\">2KI 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:3\">2CH 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:12-Job28:19\">JOB 28:12–28:19</a> <em>Wisdom cannot be bought with gold</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:9\">PSA 45:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:13\">PSA 45:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:15\">PSA 72:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:37\">PSA 105:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:15\">PRO 20:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:13\">EZK 28:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:8\">DAN 11:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:38\">DAN 11:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:4-Joel3:5\">JOL 3:4–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:20\">2TI 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:18\">REV 21:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:21\">REV 21:21</a> <em>The streets of the new Jerusalem are to be paved with gold.</em></p>\n<h2>Gold was indicative of wealth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:2\">GEN 13:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:35\">GEN 24:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:12-Deut8:14\">DEU 8:12–8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:17\">DEU 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:8\">JOS 22:8</a> <em>Joshua sends the eastern tribes home</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:13\">2KI 20:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa39:2\">ISA 39:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:15\">2CH 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27\">2CH 32:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:15\">JOB 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24-Job31:28\">JOB 31:24–31:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:8\">ECC 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:7\">ISA 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:13\">EZK 16:13</a> <em>the adornments of unfaithful Jerusalem</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:4\">EZK 28:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:18\">ZEP 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:3\">ZEC 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:14\">ZEC 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:2\">JAS 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:16\">REV 18:16</a></p>\n<h2>Gold was relatively rare</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:12\">ISA 13:12</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Gold was mined from the earth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:5-Job28:6\">JOB 28:5–28:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:11-Gen2:12\">GEN 2:11–2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Gold was refined by fire</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:18\">REV 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:21-Num31:23\">NUM 31:21–31:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:1\">JOB 28:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:3\">PRO 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:21\">PRO 27:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:9\">ZEC 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:3\">MAL 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>Gold was obtained through trade</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:22\">1KI 10:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:21\">2CH 9:21</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:26-1Kgs9:28\">1KI 9:26–9:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:17-2Chr8:18\">2CH 8:17–8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:11\">1KI 10:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:9\">2CH 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:48\">1KI 22:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:6\">ISA 60:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:9\">JER 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:22\">EZK 27:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:13\">REV 18:11–18:13</a></p>\n<h2>Gold was worked by goldsmiths</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:6\">ISA 46:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:4-1Chr29:5\">1CH 29:4–29:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:9\">JER 10:9</a></p>\n<h2>Gold was presented as offerings to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:22\">EXO 35:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:1-Exod25:7\">EXO 25:1–25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:5\">EXO 35:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:84-Num7:86\">NUM 7:84–7:86</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50-Num31:54\">NUM 31:50–31:54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:11\">2SA 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:11\">EZR 1:1–1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:12-Ezra7:18\">EZR 7:12–7:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:24-Ezra8:34\">EZR 8:24–8:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:70-Neh7:72\">NEH 7:70–7:72</a></p>\n<h2>Gold was given to rulers as tribute and bribes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:14-1Kgs10:15\">1KI 10:14–10:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:13-2Chr9:14\">2CH 9:13–9:14</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:24-1Kgs10:25\">1KI 10:24–10:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:23-2Chr9:24\">2CH 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:18\">2KI 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:7-2Kgs16:9\">2KI 16:7–16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:13-2Kgs18:16\">2KI 18:13–18:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:33-2Kgs23:35\">2KI 23:33–23:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:3\">2CH 36:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:2-2Chr16:3\">2CH 16:2–16:3</a></p>\n<h2>Gold was given as gifts</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:11\">JOB 42:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:53\">GEN 24:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:9-2Sam8:10\">2SA 8:9–8:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr18:9-1Chr18:10\">1CH 18:9–18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:10\">1KI 10:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:9\">2CH 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:5\">2KI 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:11\">MAT 2:11</a></p>\n<h2>The use of gold in the tabernacle</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:21-Exod38:24\">EXO 38:21–38:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:11-Exod25:13\">EXO 25:11–25:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:17-Exod25:18\">EXO 25:17–25:18</a> <em>the atonement cover and cherubim</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:28-Exod25:29\">EXO 25:28–25:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:31\">EXO 25:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:36\">EXO 25:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:38\">EXO 25:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:6\">EXO 26:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:29\">EXO 26:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:32\">EXO 26:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:37\">EXO 26:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:1-Exod30:5\">EXO 30:1–30:5</a> <em>the altar</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:37-Exod39:38\">EXO 39:37–39:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:5\">EXO 40:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:4\">LEV 24:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:4\">NUM 8:4</a></p>\n<h2>The use of gold in priestly vestments</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:4-Exod28:5\">EXO 28:4–28:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:11-Exod28:15\">EXO 28:11–28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:22-Exod28:27\">EXO 28:22–28:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:33-Exod28:38\">EXO 28:33–28:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:15-Exod39:20\">EXO 39:15–39:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:25-Exod39:26\">EXO 39:25–39:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:30-Exod39:31\">EXO 39:30–39:31</a></p>\n<h2>The use of gold in the temple</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:14\">1CH 22:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:28\">1KI 6:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:30\">1KI 6:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:32\">1KI 6:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:48-1Kgs7:51\">1KI 7:48–7:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:16\">2KI 18:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:14-1Chr28:18\">1CH 28:14–28:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:1-1Chr29:7\">1CH 29:1–29:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:4-2Chr3:10\">2CH 3:4–3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:7-2Chr4:8\">2CH 4:7–4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:19-2Chr4:22\">2CH 4:19–4:22</a></p>\n<h2>Gold symbols of office</h2>\n<h3>Crown</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:30\">2SA 12:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr20:2\">1CH 20:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:15\">EST 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:1-Ps21:3\">PSA 21:1–21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:11\">ZEC 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:4\">REV 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14\">REV 14:14</a></p>\n<h3>Throne</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:18-1Kgs10:20\">1KI 10:18–10:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:17-2Chr9:19\">2CH 9:17–9:19</a></p>\n<h3>Sceptre</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:11\">EST 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:2\">EST 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:4\">EST 8:4</a></p>\n<h3>Chain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:7\">DAN 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:42\">GEN 41:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:16\">DAN 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:29\">DAN 5:29</a></p>\n<h2>Other uses of gold</h2>\n<h3>Jewellery</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:22\">EXO 35:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:53\">GEN 24:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:22\">GEN 24:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:22\">EXO 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod11:2\">EXO 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:35\">EXO 12:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:2\">EXO 32:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:24\">EXO 32:24</a> <em>used to make the golden calf</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:50\">NUM 31:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:24-Judg8:26\">JDG 8:24–8:26</a> <em>used to make Gideon's ephod</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:24\">2SA 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:22\">PRO 11:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">PRO 25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:11\">SNG 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:30\">JER 4:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:5\">DAN 10:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:3\">1PE 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:23\">EXO 20:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:31\">EXO 32:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:25\">DEU 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:17\">DEU 29:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:4\">PSA 115:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:15\">PSA 135:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:20\">ISA 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:22\">ISA 30:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:7\">ISA 31:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:19\">ISA 40:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:6\">ISA 46:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:3-Jer10:5\">JER 10:3–10:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:17\">EZK 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:1\">DAN 3:1</a> <em>Nebuchadnezzar's image of gold</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:4-Dan3:7\">DAN 3:4–3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:14\">DAN 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:4\">DAN 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:4\">HOS 8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:19\">HAB 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:29\">ACT 17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20\">REV 9:20</a></p>\n<h3>Currency</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:5-Matt10:10\">MAT 10:5–10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:18\">NUM 22:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:13\">NUM 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:4\">2SA 21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:25\">1CH 21:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:72\">PSA 119:72</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:19\">EZK 7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:43\">DAN 11:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:6\">ACT 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:33\">ACT 20:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18\">1PE 1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Models</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:4\">1SA 6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:8\">1SA 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:11\">1SA 6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:15\">1SA 6:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:17-1Sam6:18\">1SA 6:17–6:18</a></p>\n<h3>Shields</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:16-1Kgs10:17\">1KI 10:16–10:17</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:15-2Chr9:16\">2CH 9:15–9:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:7\">2SA 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:26\">1KI 14:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:9\">2CH 12:9</a></p>\n<h3>Goblets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:21\">1KI 10:21</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:20\">2CH 9:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:7\">EST 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:7\">JER 51:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:2-Dan5:3\">DAN 5:2–5:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:4\">REV 17:4</a></p>\n<h3>Couches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical and proverbial use of gold</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:23-Job22:25\">JOB 22:23–22:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:8-Job23:10\">JOB 23:8–23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:9-Ps19:10\">PSA 19:9–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:13\">PSA 68:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:14\">PRO 3:13–3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:16\">PRO 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:1\">PRO 22:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">PRO 25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:10-Song5:15\">SNG 5:10–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:1-Lam4:2\">LAM 4:1–4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:37-Dan2:38\">DAN 2:37–2:38</a></p>",
